com.camerontec.util.logger.slf4j

Class Slf4jLoggerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.util.logger.slf4j.Slf4jLoggerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ILogger, org.slf4j.Logger

    public final class Slf4jLoggerAdapter
extends Object
implements ILogger
    Class for adapting an SLF4J logger to the ILogger interface.

    This implementation always delegates to an underlying SLF4J logger.
